Package: shinyburndown
Title: GitHub Issue Burndown Charts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Colin", "Diesh", email = "colin.diesh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application and CLI tool for visualizing GitHub issue
    burndown charts. Fetches issue data from any GitHub repository and generates
    various plots showing issue completion trends, time-to-close distributions,
    and open issue timelines.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
